body: Perfect compact side table.. since it's folding it is easy to store when not in use. Product had a very nice finish.. had ordered 6 tables.. so fitted perfectly as I thought them to be.. go for it ! Truly value for money !  Cons: do not use to sit on it.. can be used for light weight items only.. for heavy items, do check heavier and studier options.. just a feedback .  The table is designed for light items and works perfectly there.. so no regrets...
